ction Agenda / Marrakech Partnership and the CBD Sharm-El Sheikh to Kunming and Montreal Action Agenda for Nature and People. These are vehicles to raise ambition, drive implementation and bring coherence between both climate and nature agendas. 5 3. Flagship projects/products \u25cf Develop a CCC flagship project and product that positions the Commission, conveys the value add of the CCC, supports the decision making process, focuses on the climate and nature convergence and brings solutions that contribute to scaling up, socially just and Nature positive actions (e.g. Climate solutions evaluation framework). 4.3.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0401e2be-0919-48bd-844b-b753a3e35b05": {"__data__": {"id_": "0401e2be-0919-48bd-844b-b753a3e35b05", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-climate-crisis-commission-work-plan-2023-2024", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "IUCN Climate Crisis Commission  Work Plan 2023-2024", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-climate-crisis-commission-work-plan-2023-2024", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "6b183221b7a4bd39b304d953369e7dee832c6a9ebe06b9c48fbe14fb4217a393"}, "2": {"node_id": "7970c5d2-d1df-4b90-82a6-d4b42a0addde", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-climate-crisis-commission-work-plan-2023-2024", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "Inte